# Firebase (catalog only)

Read [`.cursor/ARCHITECTURE.md`](../ARCHITECTURE.md) → **Firebase (Firestore + Storage)** and:

- [`FIRESTORE_CATALOG_SCHEMA.md`](../../lib/features/catalog/firestore/FIRESTORE_CATALOG_SCHEMA.md)
- [`FIREBASE_STORAGE_CATALOG.md`](../../lib/features/catalog/firestore/FIREBASE_STORAGE_CATALOG.md)

## Firestore (canonical schema — do not extend)

- Use **only** existing top-level collections: `brands`, `ips`, `series`, `figures`
- Do **not** add nested hierarchies, duplicate catalog collections, or image-metadata collections
- Metadata only on docs (`imageKey`, ids, `displayName`, …) — **no** Storage URLs, **no** `imagePath`
- `loadFirestoreCatalogBundle()` — one-shot reads inside `CatalogBundleCache`; consumers use `catalogBundleProvider`, not direct Firestore calls from widgets
- **Runtime:** Firestore authoritative; persisted cache offline baseline; no APK metadata seed fallback
- Canonical ids must match filters, Storage filenames, and `imageKey` resolution (e.g. `the_monsters`, not display labels)

## Storage (canonical paths — deterministic)

- `catalog/series/<imageKey>.<ext>` and `catalog/figures/<imageKey>.<ext>`
- Build paths in `CatalogImageResolver` from `imageKey` + `CatalogImageKind` + extensions (`.avif`, `.webp`, `.png`, `.jpg`, `.jpeg`) — probe all until Storage returns an object
- Do **not** store URLs in Firestore or invent dynamic folder layouts
- Resolver order: bundled asset → Storage download URL (runtime only) → placeholder
- **Never** upload or sync `localImageUri` / `customCoverImageUri` from `features/collection/` in MVP tasks

## Boundaries

- No Firestore documents or Storage paths for user shelf state
- No `imageKey` on `ShelfFigure` / `ShelfSeries`; no Storage URLs in `CollectionSnapshotCodec`
- No `lib/services/` — code stays in `features/catalog/` + `core/firebase/`
- Canonical IP ids (e.g. `the_monsters`, not `labubu`)
- **Market:** do not load catalog bundle or `imageKey` for listing rows or card images; `MarketTaxonomy.applyCatalogBundle` is filter ids/labels only
